{"id": "1247153751937122404", "channel_id": "1247153751937122404", "type": 0, "author_id": "178779163920957440", "author_name": "rayko____", "author_bot": false, "content": "剛玩第二天，目前有這些角色\n有組出兩隊，一隊是混24、另一隊是希洛、蘿坦、艾繼絲跟羊媽的血肉隊\n有拿到羊媽專武了，想詢問接下來抽限定跟常駐的方向及其他組隊問題～\n\n1.限定有需要把羊媽補到2啟嗎？還是轉抽莉莉，羊媽用原型補？或是囤著等下個限定？\n2.不確定常駐的抽數要拿來抽什麼，補哪些角色嗎？或是命輪是否有抽取價值？\n3.如果因應關卡需要組其他隊，有什麼比較推薦的隊伍嗎？\n\n謝謝！", "timestamp": "2024-06-03T11:43:45.458000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-03T11:50:16.942000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1247153752276865045", "filename": "S__24068107.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 276036, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1247153751937122404/1247153752276865045/S__24068107.jpg?ex=6a006f71&is=69ff1df1&hm=03bb73035ed1f1e6dd0cd95384ce4ff49a7e49b09b86ce55fd59883dbc2fd4b1&"}, {"id": "1247153752667062283", "filename": "S__24068109.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 272578, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1247153751937122404/1247153752667062283/S__24068109.jpg?ex=6a006f71&is=69ff1df1&hm=9fcaf1064190affd88dfdfbcaa43e6f4c0f10bc8341923f0c2d16f01f469ff0c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247153751937122404", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "隊伍構築與抽取方向詢問", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1247104320416124989", "channel_id": "1247104320416124989", "type": 0, "author_id": "517926166569418752", "author_name": "cww8260", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-06-03T08:27:20.065000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1247104320642613311", "filename": "Screen_Recording_20240603_162613.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 1839328, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1247104320416124989/1247104320642613311/Screen_Recording_20240603_162613.mp4?ex=6a004168&is=69feefe8&hm=6abe6d9beb31b9856d8574dfb204edd8aaef0362a809a49959b0a5ea160b79ca&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247104320416124989", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」對弈-無法更換命輪", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1247074426848149587", "channel_id": "1247074426848149587", "type": 0, "author_id": "594416133210112020", "author_name": "gazima", "author_bot": false, "content": "沒玩過利茲隊，昨晚re到一個通宵到早上維修都沒有過…\n可以給點指導嗎⋯⋯\n1.覺醒是艾瑞卡》利茲、朵爾\n\n2.刻印儘量選了爆發刻在綠炎上 或是虛弱\n\n3.造物以算力為主\n\n4.超維槽大概都是綠炎1-2 誘蛾0-1 艾瑞卡防禦 艾瑞卡武裝 \n\n5.賣卡賣小騎士的攻擊與穿刺，不賣朵爾的3費是想說打王可以消掉鬼牌（但好像沒有用…）\n\n6.落地、道中 流程大略是虛弱》疊盾〉能小暴發就清道剩一隻讓自己補血與控超維保持下一場戰鬥超維空間有可以3-5張可以用\n\n7.打王會儘量不丟誘蛾 那個次數+鬼牌 手牌直接炸裂\n\n8.朵爾3費打王是不是內鬼啊 丟完抽牌堆都是綠炎跟鬼牌 \n\n9.覺醒利茲綠炎打王時要怎麼合理運用？算力拿去頂打擊防禦衝狂氣與艾瑞卡的盾跟小騎士的壁壘就不夠了⋯⋯", "timestamp": "2024-06-03T06:28:32.883000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1247074427728957481", "filename": "IMG_2538.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1941621, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1247074426848149587/1247074427728957481/IMG_2538.png?ex=6a00ce51&is=69ff7cd1&hm=c8cbae60a4def9f177d40d851a00dcd076c80bdc3e6895d1db897306440fdebd&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247074426848149587", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "有大佬可以幫忙看一下我融災3-2的莉茲隊嗎", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1186103872205369424"]}
